column2: SELECT    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,   s.class,s.subclass, s.z,g.specObjID , s.specObjID, s.z as redshift,   g.h_beta_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux into some_data from dr1#.PhotoObjAll AS p     JOIN dr1#.SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid     JOIN MyDB.Objects AS m ON m.specobjid = s.bestobjid     JOIN dr1#.galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID
